    <h3>Register/Login</h3>
    <p>Users can create an account or log in with their credentials to access all the available functionalities.</p>

    <h3>Schedule Appointments</h3>
    <p>Users can schedule appointments with veterinarians, selecting the desired date and time.</p>

    <h3>Access Medical Records</h3>
    <p>Users can view and manage their pet's medical history and records.</p>

    <h3>Telemedicine Consultations</h3>
    <p>Users can request telemedicine consultations with veterinarians, allowing them to discuss their pet's health remotely.</p>

    <h3>Order Medications and Supplies</h3>
    <p>Users can order medications, pet food, and other supplies conveniently through the platform.</p>

    <h3>Find Veterinarians and Clinics</h3>
    <p>Users can search for veterinarians and clinics near their location, access reviews and ratings, and make appointments.</p>

    <h3>Get Pet Health Tips and Articles</h3>
    <p>Users can access a range of pet health tips, articles, and educational resources to help them take better care of their pets.</p>
